data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the growing community of Stead. The living room is a space of comfort and warmth. Natural light floods the room, accentuating the panoramic views of the front yard and majestic mountains beyond. The dining room and kitchen combo form the heart of the home. Designed for seamless integration, this layout ensures you never miss out on conversations while sitting down for a hot meal. The 3 bedrooms offer great space and the perfect place to unwind, with brand new carpet installed 2023. With ample room for outdoor activities, gatherings, and relaxation, the yard space is perfect to create memorable moments under the sun or stars. The concrete area is tailor-made for summer BBQs and al fresco entertainment, promising cherished times with friends and family. Brand new furnace installed in 2022. Listing agent is the owner and has a NV Real Estate License.
